Package com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame Description

Advanced functions such as dithering, VLC C++ interaction can be found here. You may ask why I could've just made a default VideoPlayer and make it accept any callback possible. While this is possible, I would like to still provide an abstraction for the actual video player itself just in case that we need to add, remove, or modify existing features.
